Package: razer
Title: Light Agent Spatial Modeling for Eradication (R)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Christopher", "Lorton", , "christopher.lorton@gatesfoundation.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R interface to the LASER (Light Agent Spatial modeling for ERadication)
    toolkit. Provides high-performance, Rust-backed data structures and
    epidemiological components for large-scale spatial agent-based disease
    models, including struct-of-arrays population frames, migration network
    models, and composable SEIR-family compartmental model components.
